# Basic BGP Configuration

This workspace contains the following files and folders:

- R1 configuration file
- R2 configuration file
-topology diagram
This file to describe the subnet plan for the topology.
It includes network prefixes, mask lengths, and router-facing interfaces.
A /30 point-to-point link using 10.0.12.0/30.

Topology assumption:
R1 fa0/0: 10.0.12.1/30
R2 fa0/0: 10.0.12.2/30
